-50!
-I beg your pardon?

107
00:12:04,183 --> 00:12:07,017
-650.
-To 650! Of course!

108
00:12:07,725 --> 00:12:11,119
Of course! Always convenient, a few
razor blades and some toothpaste.

109
00:12:11,143 --> 00:12:13,494
-Just add on everything.
-Yes, big boxes.

110
00:12:13,518 --> 00:12:17,102
-My pleasure.
-All in all 650, here, please.

111
