since we founded the company.

122
00:13:00,603 --> 00:13:04,309
Is that so? Who was out for breakfast with
the bailiff last time? Me!

123
00:13:06,143 --> 00:13:08,059
-Do you know what you are?
-You're it yourself.

124
00:13:15,975 --> 00:13:18,059
-Yuck!
-What's the matter?

125
00:13:18,433 --> 00:13:20,684
-This is soap!
-What are you saying?

126
00:13:22,008 --> 00:13:23,008
A mix-up.

127
00:13:26,476 --> 00:13:29,642
Correct.
You got the bad end of the stick, though.

128
00:13:35,642 --> 00:13:40,268
-Did you find a job for me?
-Yes. Someone's looking for a lift boy.

129
00:13:40,434 --> 00:13:42,935
I can do that. Take notes.

130
00:13:43,976 --> 00:13:48,308
