What have you done with the register?
It won't open.

181
00:19:00,352 --> 00:19:02,369
-What do you mean?
-What did you do with it?

182
00:19:02,393 --> 00:19:03,476
Let me look at it.

183
00:19:06,225 --> 00:19:10,683
I don't get it.
Hasn't been used in a while.

184
00:19:13,268 --> 00:19:16,642
Rusty... Here we go!

185
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:18,393
That's the telephone.

186
00:19:21,518 --> 00:19:23,976
-Hello there?
-Do I speak with Florida?

187
00:19:26,183 --> 00:19:28,465
"Longing 202" speaking.

188
