 I would've written you one.

218
00:21:25,937 --> 00:21:27,979
Or two, or three,
makes no difference to me.

219
00:21:29,392 --> 00:21:31,600
Say, do you always talk so much trash?

220
00:21:32,193 --> 00:21:34,938
No, only when I'm in a good mood.

221
00:21:36,311 --> 00:21:39,433
So you're in an especially good mood today.

222
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:46,475
What a girl!
♫ Longing 202

223
00:21:47,771 --> 00:21:50,454
